You must : 

1 - replace WHPP\WHPP-ejb\src\main\resources\META-INF\persistence.xml to your real  datasource in
<jta-data-source>jdbc/__default</jta-data-source>

2 - set Table Generation Strategy to "Drop and create" in WHPP\WHPP-ejb\src\main\resources\META-INF\persistence.xml design

